  "subject": "Toggle",
  "commit_message": "Toggle\n\n- Move existing toggling classes to common-be.\n- Add HEALING feature to ToggleableFeature class, in order to control this feature using toggle mechanism.\n- Add a check in HealJanusGraphDao class if HEALING feature is enabled, and call to healing process accordingly.\n- Change javax.ws.rs version to 2.1, in order for it to work with togglz packages, and change Response.class usage to avoid runtime errors.\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-2874\nSigned-off-by: talio <talio@amdocs.com>\nChange-Id: I73d152437476b1cb83211608845292d5a6b7af2d\nSigned-off-by: talio <talio@amdocs.com>\n",
